# Project Context
- This is a Next.js app deployed on Vercel with Supabase as the backend.
- Use TypeScript strictly. No `any` types.
- Use functional components and React hooks.

# Deployment
- Use Vercel MCP to check deployment status and logs.
- Use GitHub MCP to create PRs and manage issues.
- After making code changes in this repo, run `npm run build` to ensure the Next.js production build and TypeScript checks pass before considering the task complete.

# Database
- Always use Supabase MCP to verify schema before writing migrations.
- Use Row Level Security (RLS) on all tables.